- JWT-based access tokens with configurable expiry (default 24h consumer, 8h institutional)
- Refresh token rotation — every refresh invalidates the previous token
- Device fingerprinting for session binding
- Concurrent session limits — configurable maximum active sessions per user
- Session revocation API — immediate invalidation for compliance and incident response
- Complete audit trail — every auth event logged with immutable timestamps

