#### 2.3 Wallet Module (`@partylayer/enterprise-wallet`)

The wallet module handles the full lifecycle of Canton wallets — creation, signing, recovery — using a server-side custodial architecture with an upgrade path to MPC threshold signatures.

**Server-Side Key Management Architecture**

